ht:var(--font-normal); --ticker-hover2-box-shadow:0 4px 10px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .08); --ticker-hover2-border-color:var(--light-divider);\"><span class=\"ticker-wrapper yf-hwu3c7 has-follow\"><a data-testid=\"ticker-container\" class=\"ticker medium    hover2   border  has-follow streaming  extraPadding yf-hwu3c7\" aria-label=\"BRBR\" data-ylk=\"elm:qte;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:ticker-tag-module;slk:BRBR\" href=\"/quote/BRBR/\" title=\"BRBR\"> <div class=\"name yf-hwu3c7\"> <span class=\"symbol yf-hwu3c7\">BRBR </span> </div> <fin-streamer class=\"percentChange yf-hwu3c7\" data-symbol=\"BRBR\" data-field=\"regularMarketChangePercent\" data-trend=\"txt\" data-pricehint=\"2\" data-tstyle=\"default\" active><span class=\"txt-negative yf-hwu3c7\">-1.61%</span></fin-streamer> </a> <div class=\"follow yf-hwu3c7 extraPadding\"><div data-testid=\"lazy-render\"></div> <button data-testid=\"follow-btn-loading\" class=\"placeholder-btn extra-padding yf-li9b97\" aria-label=\"Follow\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon fin-icon tertiary-icn sz-medium  yf-1iuxsdd\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m22 9.24-7.19-.62L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21 12 17.27 18.18 21l-1.63-7.03zM12 15.4l-3.76 2.27 1-4.28-3.32-2.88 4.38-.38L12 6.1l1.71 4.04 4.38.38-3.32 2.88 1 4.28z\"></path></svg><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></div></button></div></span></div></div></div> </div></div></div>  <div class=\"body yf-1ir6o1g\">   <div class=\"atoms-wrapper\">   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->BellRing Brands, Inc. (NYSE:<a href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BRBR\" data-ylk=\"slk:BRBR;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">BRBR</a>) is one of¬†<strong><a href=\"https://www.insidermonkey.com/blog/10-consumer-defensive-stocks-to-buy-now-1559291/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:10 consumer defensive stocks to buy now;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">10 consumer defensive stocks to buy now</a>.¬†</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Mizuho analyst has adjusted the price target on BellRing Brands, Inc. (NYSE:BRBR) to $75 from $85, while maintaining an Outperform rating. The revision comes amid an industry-wide valuation reset in the food producer sector, prompting the firm to recalibrate its expectations for BellRing alongside peers.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <figure class=\"yf-8xybrv\"><div class=\"image-container yf-1gfnohs loader\" style=\"--max-height: 538px;\"> <div class=\"image-wrapper yf-1gfnohs\" style=\"--aspect-ratio: 960 / 538; --img-max-width: 960px;\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///ywAAAAAAQABAAACAUwAOw==\" alt=\"Mizuho Trims BellRing (BRBR) Price Target, Maintains Outperform Rating\" loading=\"eager\" height=\"538\" width=\"960\" class=\"yf-1gfnohs loader\"></div></div> <figcaption class=\"yf-8xybrv\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Mizuho Trims BellRing (BRBR) Price Target, Maintains Outperform Rating<!-- HTML_TAG_END -->  </figcaption> </figure>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->A wide shot of an aisle in a food store lined with different nutrition products.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Despite the lower target, Mizuho remains positive about BellRing‚Äôs prospects. The company‚Äôs recent expansion efforts, particularly increased distribution across retail channels, continue to support near-term growth. Analysts also noted the buoyancy of the nutrition category, where BellRing Brands, Inc. (NYSE:BRBR) holds a strong position with its core brands. Additionally, the company has limited exposure to private-label competition, bolstering its pricing power and margin resilience.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <div class=\"wrapper yf-eondll\" data-testid=\"inarticle-ad\">  <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-6195f22f-4bba-3801-a701-15485968d007-1\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-6195f22f-4bba-3801-a701-15485968d007-1 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250,fluid\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div></div>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Mizuho‚Äôs industry review prompted valuation adjustments across several food stocks, but the analyst emphasized that BellRing retains structural advantages. The diversified flavor-infusion portfolio and robust growth in categories like shake-based nutrition offerings provide a foundation for sustained performance. BellRing‚Äôs ability to expand shelf presence and execute within fast-growing segments aligns well with Mizuho‚Äôs top-pick criteria, even as general sector sentiment softens.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Analysts expect BellRing to outperform the broader sector in volume and revenue growth, with the valuation adjustment offering a more compelling entry point. Mizuho‚Äôs maintained Outperform rating indicates sustained confidence in BellRing‚Äôs business model amidst evolving market valuations.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <div class=\"wrapper yf-eondll\" data-testid=\"inarticle-ad\">  <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-6195f22f-4bba-3801-a701-15485968d007-2\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-6195f22f-4bba-3801-a701-15485968d007-2 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_2\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div></div>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->While we acknowledge the potential of BRBR to grow, our conviction lies in the belief that some AI stocks hold greater promise for delivering higher returns and have limited downside risk. If you are looking for an AI stock that is more promising than BRBR and that has 100x upside potential, check out our report about this¬†<a href=\"https://www.insidermonkey.com/blog/undervalued-ai-stock-poised-for-massive-gains-10000-upside-17/?forcedCTACode=PR24J\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:cheapest AI stock.;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \"><strong>cheapest AI stock.</strong></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><b>READ NEXT:¬†</b><strong><a href=\"https://www.insidermonkey.com/blog/15-best-dividend-stocks-of-2025-1558912/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:15 Best Dividend Stocks of 2025;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">15 Best Dividend Stocks of 2025</a></strong><b>¬†and¬†<a href=\"https://www.insidermonkey.com/blog/10-best-wide-moat-dividend-stocks-to-invest-in-1557631/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:10 Best Wide Moat Dividend Stocks to Invest in;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">10 Best Wide Moat Dividend Stocks to Invest in</a>.</b><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Disclosure: None. Insider Monkey focuses on uncovering the best investment ideas of hedge funds and insiders. Please subscribe to our free daily e-newsletter to get the latest investment ideas from hedge funds‚Äô investor letters by entering your email address below.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> </div>     </div></div> <span class=\"article-footer yf-10hzt8r\"><section class=\"privacy-container yf-1uw5cxs inline\" style=\"--privacy-link-font-weight: var(--font-normal);\"><div class=\"terms-and-privacy small yf-1uw5cxs column\"><a class=\"subtle-link fin-size-small privacy-link-terms-link     yf-u4gyzs\" data-ylk=\"elm:corp;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:article;subsec:footer\" href=\"https://guce.yahoo.com/terms?locale=en-US\">Terms  </a> and <