(147,'Yahoo Finance','The Clorox Company (NYSE:CLX) is one of 10 consumer defensive stocks to buy now. Jefferies has adjusted its price target on The Clorox Company (NYSE:CLX) to $145 from $167, while maintaining a Buy rating on the stock. In its latest research note, the firm warned that the next two quarters ‚Äúwill be complicated to model‚Äù due [‚Ä¶]','<article class=\"gridLayout yf-plaft0\">  <div class=\"article yf-l7apfj\">  <div class=\"article-wrap no-bb\" data-testid=\"article-content-wrapper\"> <div class=\"cover-wrap yf-1rjrr1\"> <div class=\"top-header yf-1rjrr1\">  <a class=\"subtle-link fin-size-small      yf-u4gyzs\" data-ylk=\"elm:logo;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:logo-provider;slk:Insider%20Monkey\" href=\"http://www.insidermonkey.com\" aria-label=\"Insider Monkey\" title=\"Insider Monkey\"><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LZG2ouUXGgu63htqYbzXgA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNjtoPTQ4O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/d7df1000-34e4-11eb-b6ae-ac87660fe5ee\" alt=\"Insider Monkey\" width=\"63\" height=\"24\" loading=\"lazy\">  </a> </div> <div class=\"cover-headline yf-1rjrr1\"><h1 class=\"cover-title yf-1rjrr1\">Jefferies Trims Clorox (CLX) Price Target, Maintains Buy Rating</h1> <label class=\" type-ui-xxl-reg    yf-gjjls9\"> </label></div>  </div> <div class=\"byline yf-1k5w6kz\"><div class=\"byline-attr yf-1k5w6kz\"> <div><div class=\"byline-attr-author yf-1k5w6kz\">  Sanmit Amin </div> <div class=\"byline-attr-time-style\"> <time class=\"byline-attr-meta-time\" datetime=\"2025-06-29T07:02:47.000Z\" data-timestamp=\"2025-06-29T07:02:47.000Z\">Sun, Jun 29, 2025, 3:02 PM</time> <span class=\"byline-attr-mins-read yf-37lelh\">2 min read</span></div></div></div> <div class=\"byline-share yf-1k5w6kz\"><div><span class=\"share-dialog yf-15ypo5z\"><div class=\"menuContainer  yf-1l5q6k1\" style=\"                    \"><button class=\"tertiary-btn fin-size-medium menuBtn tw-p-1  rounded   yf-1epmntv\" data-ylk=\"elmt:menu;