(154,'Yahoo News','The latest news and headlines from Yahoo News. Get breaking news stories and in-depth coverage with videos and photos.','<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Florida is one of the worst states in the US when it comes to access to affordable dental care ‚Äì and children are suffering as a result.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">While trying to conceive, learning and memory researcher Liz Chrastil took an unusual step: She became her own subject in a study of how pregnancy changes the brain.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">PARATY, Brazil - My son had a high fever, so my wife and I decided to cut short our beach vacation and head home, worried about the quality of health care so far from Rio de Janeiro. I packed our bags, took one last look at the calm shoreline and headed out to load up the car. I popped open the trunk door of our hatchback and commenced with that intricate game of Tetris practiced by all vacation dads.Subscribe to The Post Most newsletter for the most important and interesting stories from The Wa</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Our ancient ancestors didn‚Äôt have clothes or houses ‚Äì but that constant exposure to the sun helped their skin protect itself from the worst sun damage.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Some tattoo inks contain unlabeled materials that can cause allergic reactions.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Major heat waves across southern Europe have pushed temperatures above 40 C (104 F) in countries including Italy, Spain and Greece, as local authorities issued fresh warnings against the risk of wildfires.  Experts link the rising frequency and intensity of these heat waves to climate change, warning that such extreme weather events are becoming increasingly common across Europe\'s southern region.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Try these health tips to have your best week yet.</p>','https://www.yahoo.com/news/health/','2025-06-30 15:28:37'),
