(162,'Yahoo News','The latest news and headlines from Yahoo News. Get breaking news stories and in-depth coverage with videos and photos.','<p class=\"LineClamp(4,5.700em)!--miw1200 LineClamp(3,4.30em) Lh(1.43) Mx(0) Mt(0) Mb(4px) Fz(14px)!--miw1300 Fz(12px) Cur(p)\" data-test-locator=\"lead-summary\">The price tag has received plenty of additional attention after a new weekend tally found that the bill has grown by nearly $1 trillion since the Senate took it up.</p>\n<p aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"Fz(14px)!--miw1300 Fz(12px) LineClamp(1,1.3em) Fw(b)!--miw1300 Fw(600) C(--hulk-pants):h Cur(p) Pos(r) Z(1)\"> Read More¬†¬ª</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">The Supreme Court on Monday threw out appellate rulings in favor of transgender people in four states following the justices\' recent decision upholding a Tennessee ban on certain medical treatment for transgender youths.  The high court ordered appellate judges to reexamine cases from Idaho, North Carolina, Oklahoma and West Virginia involving access to medical care and birth certificates.  The rulings all included findings that the restrictions on transgender people imposed by the states violat</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">ALERT: Traffic was delayed on I-70 after a windmill blade fell across the highway, blocking multiple lanes in both directions Monday morning. Drivers traveling in this area are encouraged to follow police directions and use caution.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">The anchor responded to the president\'s rage post with six words.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Mullin\'s comments on NBC\'s \"Meet the Press\" came in response to questions about a U.S. Supreme Court decision on Friday that paved the way for President Donald Trump\'s executive order restricting birthright citizenship to go into effect soon in some states.  The court\'s ruling did not address the legality of Trump\'s order, which would upend the historic practice of granting U.S. citizenship to anyone born in the country regardless of their parents\' immigration status.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">The California Highway Patrol responded to a call this week of a possible baby tiger stranded on the side of a highway in San Luis Obispo County.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">The creatures can grow up to 5 feet long.</p>\n<p class=\"finance-ticker-fetch-success_D(n) LineClamp(2,40px) sub-upsell-fetch-success_D(n) Fz(14px) Lh(1.43) C(--batcave) Mb(4px) Mend(50px) Mt(2px) Bxz(bb) Wob($break-word)\" data-test-locator=\"stream-item-summary\">Retzlaff\'s contention that he had consensual sex with his accuser would be a violation of BYU\'s honor code, which prohibits premarital sex.</p>','https://www.yahoo.com/news/','2025-06-30 15:28:39'),
(163,'Yahoo Finance','HANOI (Reuters) -Vietnamese electric vehicle manufacturer VinFast began production on Sunday at its second domestic factory, aiming to ramp up output of affordable mini urban models as its global expansion plans face delays.  The new facility, located in the central province of Ha Tinh, has an initial annual capacity of 200,000 units and spans 36 hectares (90 acres), the company said in a statement.  VinFast, backed by Vietnam\'s largest conglomerate Vingroup, has set ambitious goals to establish','<article class=\"gridLayout yf-plaft0\">  <div class=\"article yf-l7apfj\">  <div class=\"article-wrap no-bb\" data-testid=\"article-content-wrapper\"> <div class=\"cover-wrap yf-1rjrr1\"> <div class=\"top-header yf-1rjrr1\">  <a class=\"subtle-link fin-size-small      yf-u4gyzs\" data-ylk=\"elm:logo;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:logo-provider;slk:Reuters\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/\" aria-label=\"Reuters\" title=\"Reuters\"><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tMoAFlP_ZOG3JMrIhrjnuQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTIwNjtoPTQ4O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/62e21440-2fbd-11eb-95ff-5673fa3d2f9f\" alt=\"Reuters\" width=\"103\" height=\"24\" loading=\"lazy\">  </a> </div> <div class=\"cover-headline yf-1rjrr1\"><h1 class=\"cover-title yf-1rjrr1\">VinFast opens second domestic EV factory amid global expansion</h1> <label class=\" type-ui-xxl-reg    yf-gjjls9\"> </label></div> <figure class=\"yf-8xybrv\"><div class=\"image-container yf-1gfnohs loader\" style=\"--max-height: 533px;\"> <div class=\"image-wrapper yf-1gfnohs\" style=\"--aspect-ratio: 800 / 533; --img-max-width: 800px;\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///ywAAAAAAQABAAACAUwAOw==\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"533\" width=\"800\" class=\"yf-1gfnohs loader\"></div></div> <figcaption class=\"yf-8xybrv\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->India\'s five-day auto show in New Delhi<!-- HTML_TAG_END --> <span class=\"caption-separator yf-8xybrv\" data-svel