as-follow streaming  extraPadding yf-hwu3c7\" aria-label=\"GOOGL\" data-ylk=\"elm:qte;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:ticker-tag-module;slk:GOOGL\" href=\"/quote/GOOGL/\" title=\"GOOGL\"> <div class=\"name yf-hwu3c7\"> <span class=\"symbol yf-hwu3c7\">GOOGL </span> </div> <fin-streamer class=\"percentChange yf-hwu3c7\" data-symbol=\"GOOGL\" data-field=\"regularMarketChangePercent\" data-trend=\"txt\" data-pricehint=\"2\" data-tstyle=\"default\" active><span class=\"txt-negative yf-hwu3c7\">-1.13%</span></fin-streamer> </a> <div class=\"follow yf-hwu3c7 extraPadding\"><div data-testid=\"lazy-render\"></div> <button data-testid=\"follow-btn-loading\" class=\"placeholder-btn extra-padding yf-li9b97\" aria-label=\"Follow\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon fin-icon tertiary-icn sz-medium  yf-1iuxsdd\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"m22 9.24-7.19-.62L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21 12 17.27 18.18 21l-1.63-7.03zM12 15.4l-3.76 2.27 1-4.28-3.32-2.88 4.38-.38L12 6.1l1.71 4.04 4.38.38-3.32 2.88 1 4.28z\"></path></svg><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></div></button></div></span></div></div></div> </div></div></div>  <div class=\"body yf-1ir6o1g\">   <div class=\"atoms-wrapper\">   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->President Trump said in an interview that aired Sunday that he <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-says-doesn-t-expect-152200922.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:did not plan to extend the July 9 tariff deadline;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">did not plan to extend the July 9 tariff deadline </a>he set for countries to broker deals with the US, while Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent warned countries that they could face a return to steep \"Liberation Day\" levels.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôll need to,\" he told Fox News‚Äôs Maria Bartiromo. He added, however: \"I could, no big deal.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <div class=\"wrapper yf-eondll\" data-testid=\"inarticle-ad\">  <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-1\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-1 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250,fluid\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div></div>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bessent said countries being \"recalcitrant\" could see tariff levels jump back up.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"We have countries that are negotiating in good faith, but they should be aware that if we can\'t get across the line because they are being recalcitrant, then we could spring back to the April 2 levels,\" he said during a Bloomberg interview.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The comments were the latest signs of ambiguity around the self-imposed deadline, when Trump\'s \"pause\" on his April 2 duties expires. Trump himself and administration officials have sent mixed signals about the firmness of the deadline as it fast approaches.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <div class=\"wrapper yf-eondll\" data-testid=\"inarticle-ad\">  <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-2\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-2 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_2\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div></div>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Meanwhile, <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/canada-rescinds-digital-services-tax-022509913.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:late on Sunday;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">late on Sunday</a>, Canada scrapped its digital services tax on US technology companies, such as Apple (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL\" data-ylk=\"slk:AAPL;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">AAPL</a>), Amazon (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN\" data-ylk=\"slk:AMZN;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">AMZN</a>) and Alphabet (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/GOOG\" data-ylk=\"slk:GOOG;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">GOOG</a>, <a data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/GOOGL\" data-ylk=\"slk:GOOGL;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">GOOGL</a>), just hours before it was set to start. The White House said trade talks between the two countries had resumed after Trump threatened to cut off trade talks.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The abrupt shift in US-Canada relations followed a flurry of optimism on the trade front that helped <a data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/live/stock-market-today-sp-500-nasdaq-head-for-records-as-trade-talks-fed-rate-cut-bets-boost-spirits-133539202.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:send stocks to new records on Friday;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">send stocks to new records on Friday</a>. Most notably, the US and China stepped closer to a full tariff and trade deal, making a pact to formally cement the informal trade understanding reached in Geneva talks in May.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>    <div class=\"loader  yf-1xkg2e5\" style=\"height: 480px\"></div> <div class=\"flourish-container  yf-1xkg2e5\" data-src=\"visualisation/22449129\" data-testid=\"flourish-container\"></div>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Countries from <a data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/pressure-seal-trump-trade-deals-082640465.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Canada to Japan;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Canada to Japan</a> are struggling to <a data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/pressure-seal-trump-trade-deals-082640465.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:get over the finish line;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">get over the finish line</a> on deals just over one week until the deadline. Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent hinted at progress on US talks with its most important partners.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"I think we could have trade wrapped up by Labor Day,\" Bessent said in a Fox Business interview.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->So far, Trump has only firmed up one signed <a data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/im-a-tariff-person-trump-searching-for-new-trade-deals-in-canada-as-liberation-day-20-deadline-draws-closer-170808647.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:trade deal with the United Kingdom;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">trade deal with the United Kingdom</a>.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><em>Read more: </em><a data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/personal-finance/taxes/article/what-is-a-tariff-194059448.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:What Trump\'s tariffs mean for the economy and your wallet;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>What Trump\'s tariffs mean for the economy and your wallet</em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Here are the latest updates as the policy reverberates around the world.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <span class=\"caas-live-blog-section-badge isLive yf-jncdpv\">LIVE</span> <span class=\"caas-live-blog-section-badge-count yf-jncdpv\">1285 updates</span> <div class=\"liveblog-posts yf-jncdpv show-more-active\"><ul class=\"caas-liveblog-pinned-list\" data-testid=\"pinned-blog-posts\"><li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb pinned\" id=\"70f08e8f-a39d-48e5-a38c-3ef9040ebe5b\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"pinned-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"label yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"pinned-label-icon yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"file-action-pin yf-1ebdqmb\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"icon fin-icon primary-icn sz-x-large  yf-1iuxsdd\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M14 4v5c0 1.12.37 2.16 1 3H9c.65-.86 1-1.9 1-3V4zm3-2H7c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1h1v5c0 1.66-1.34 3-3 3v2h5.97v7l1 1 1-1v-7H19v-2c-1.66 0-3-1.34-3-3V4h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1\"></path></svg><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></div></div> <div class=\"post-featured yf-1ebdqmb\">Featured</div></div></div> <div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post-header yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 8:37 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div></div> <div class=\"content yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"headline-block yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Canada rescinds digital services tax to advance stalled US trade talks</h2> </div> <div class=\"content-block yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/canada-rescinds-digital-services-tax-022509913.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Canada scrapped its;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Canada scrapped its</a> planned digital services tax on US tech firms late Sunday, just hours before it was due to start.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The move aims to revive stalled trade talks with the US, which halted on Friday over the tax, with President Trump calling it a \"blatant attack.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/canada-rescinds-digital-services-tax-022509913.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Canada\'s finance;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Canada\'s finance</a> ministry said Prime Minister Mark Carney and Trump plan to reach a deal by July 21.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/canada-rescinds-digital-services-tax-022509913.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Trump warned on Friday;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Trump warned on Friday</a> he would set new tariffs on Canadian goods within a week, risking fresh tension between the two countries.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The 3% tech tax would have hit firms like Apple (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL\" data-ylk=\"slk:AAPL;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">AAPL</a>), Google (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/GOOG\" data-ylk=\"slk:GOOG;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">GOOG</a>), and Amazon (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN\" data-ylk=\"slk:AMZN;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">AMZN</a>), but Canada will now bring forward legislation to cancel it.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"The DST was announced in 2020 to address the fact that many large technology companies operating in Canada may not otherwise pay tax on revenues generated from Canadians,\" a statement from the Canadian <a data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/canada-rescinds-digital-services-tax-022509913.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:finance ministry said.;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">finance ministry said.</a> \"Canada‚Äôs preference has always been a multilateral agreement related to digital services taxation.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li></ul>  <ul class=\"liveblog-list yf-jncdpv\" data-testid=\"blog-posts\"><li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"ce2dcf66-97df-4919-b1dc-8b563c36f1d5\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 1:24 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Tariffs start to bite as US prices of China-made goods jump on Amazon</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Tariffs pressures have started to hit goods, with prices on products made in China sold on Amazon (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN\" data-ylk=\"slk:AMZN;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">AMZN</a>) rising faster than overall inflation, according to 1,400 different items which were analysed by DataWeave and provided exclusively to Reuters.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>  <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Reuters reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>     <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/us-prices-china-made-goods-120556419.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here.;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here. </em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"acd91f6b-94a4-4b12-a254-6fbd2fa8bce6\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 12:48 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">This could be the summer of economic hell</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/could-summer-economic-hell-090025705.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:CNN reports:;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">CNN reports: </a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>    <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/could-summer-economic-hell-090025705.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here.;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here. </em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"f6179f9d-04cb-4c9d-8318-f7ce24fb3173\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 11:45 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">EU Commission: EU tech rules not included in US trade talks</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The European Union is pushing back against the US and its criticism of the bloc\'s tech rules, which many feared may have been included as part of trade negotiations.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Reuters reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>     <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.yahoo.com/news/eu-tech-rules-not-included-104211690.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here.;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here. </em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>   <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-3\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-3 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_3\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div> <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"f2140b9c-7277-4627-90d5-7e531205fd51\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 11:30 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Fed versus Trump on tariffs impact will soon be put to the test</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->There is a belief among economists that President Trump\'s tariffs will help boost inflation over the next few months. But so far, muted price increases have called that belief into question. This has helped to embolden Trump, causing divisions with the Fed.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bloomberg News reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>    <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/fed-versus-trump-tariffs-impact-100000504.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here.;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here. </em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"3c324020-17f0-49fb-a858-bd1254daf58c\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 10:50 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Trading partners brace for US tariff deadlines</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/south-korea-says-seeking-extension-070123086.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:South Korea;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">South Korea</a> is looking for an extension to the July 9 tariff deadline as talks continue. The US has raised concerns over non-tariff barriers and broader defence. South Korea is not the only country looking to reach a deal with the US before the tariff <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/south-korea-says-seeking-extension-070123086.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:deadline on July 9.;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">deadline on July 9.</a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"It seems some countries will reach a deal by July 8, some might be granted an extension to continue negotiations, while others will decide if they want to continue negotiating under tariffs or not,\" the South Korean official told a briefing.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Here\'s how some of the other trading partners are managing the deadline.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>  <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><strong>China</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The US and China reached a deal to resume <a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/chinas-rare-earths-flowing-again-152849343.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:rare earth exports in London this month,;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">rare earth exports in London this month, </a>resolving delays in implementing the Geneva agreement, which was established in May. Both sides are keen to ease tensions before tariffs rise further on August 9, when broader duties could rise 50%.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><strong>Canada</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/canada-rescinds-digital-services-tax-022509913.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Canada scrapped its planned digital services;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Canada scrapped its planned digital services</a> tax targeting US tech firms on Sunday in an attempt to revive stalled talks. President Trump threatened new tariffs within a week if no deal is reached. According to Reuters, talks aim for an agreement by July 21.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><strong>EU</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->EU negotiators are pushing to <a data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/eu-increasingly-resigned-10-baseline-115951577.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:keep reciprocal tariffs;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">keep reciprocal tariffs</a> below 10% but Washington is pursuing a 10% baseline rate on most goods. Talks continue as the EU faces a looming <a data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" href=\"https://uk.finance.yahoo.com/news/eu-received-latest-trade-proposal-234713883.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:deadline of July 9.;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">deadline of July 9. </a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><strong>UK</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The <a data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/deal-reduced-us-tariffs-uk-044719029.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:US-UK trade deal was cemented;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">US-UK trade deal was cemented </a>at the G-7 Summit this month. The deal came into <a data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/deal-reduced-us-tariffs-uk-044719029.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:force this week,;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">force this week,</a> reducing levies on cars and aircraft parts but keeping 10% tariffs on exports. Steel and aluminium tariffs remain unresloved ahead of the July 9 deadline.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><strong>Japan</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Japan is seeking exemption from <a data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-says-mr-japan-unfair-072346703.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:US auto tariffs,;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">US auto tariffs,</a> which currently stand at 25%, while also facing a new 24% reciprocal tariff from July 9. Trump wants Japan to import more US energy to reduce its trade surplus.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><strong>Mexico</strong><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/us-mexico-close-deal-cut-204158891.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:The US and Mexico;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">The US and Mexico</a> are negotiating a quota deal to reduce Trump\'s 50% steel tariffs. An agreement may allow for lower import rates.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"ec265d47-c1de-41e0-a146-4732cd937aa4\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Mu961r2aioIDU88sl1pWxA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fimage_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2024-10%252F82cf5f80-8bd8-11ef-babf-b4e662504245%26compress%3D1%26progressive%3D1%26quality%3D75%26client%3Dhawkeye%26signature%3Deba9c6bf409177b1a8c7fa8257231200b686e99c&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=839dce8d897765d2f2bd1f7dbbf52134bb20dcb4\" alt=\"Jenny McCall\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Today at 9:08 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Jenny McCall</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Goldman: US profit margins face key risk from tariffs</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->As earning season approaches, Goldman Sachs (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/GS\" data-ylk=\"slk:GS;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">GS</a>) said on Monday that US profit margins will be tested as investors await to see how President Trump\'s war has hurt companies.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Goldman\'s David Kostin said Q2 earnings will show the immediate impact of tariffs, which have risen about 10% this year. Most costs will be passed on to consumers, but margins will suffer if firms absorb more than expected.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Early results are mixed: General Mills (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/GIS\" data-ylk=\"slk:GIS;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">GIS</a>) stock fell 5% last week due to a weak forecast and tariff warning, while Nike (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NKE\" data-ylk=\"slk:NKE;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">NKE</a>) rose 15% after announcing it will offset higher duties.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bloomberg News reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>  <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/us-profit-margins-face-key-074559771.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here.;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here. </em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>   <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-4\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-4 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_4\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div> <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"a7602880-6973-4ec6-b70c-eece64716be3\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Sun, June 29, 2025 at 8:44 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Bloomberg</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">With 10 days to go, Trump admin coming up short of predicted tariff deals</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Despite predictions from members of President Trump\'s administration that it could complete \"90 deals in 90 days,\" the White House doesn\'t appear to be anywhere close to the sweeping global trade reform it was seeking, Bloomberg reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>   <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-deals-poised-fall-short-200000167.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here</em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"30fa0090-ce95-4f12-b47d-d6b6c5688f9f\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Sun, June 29, 2025 at 4:18 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Bloomberg</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">\'I don\'t think I\'ll need to\': Trump not planning to extend July 9 tariff deadline</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->In a wide-ranging interview during which he also said he had a <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-says-buyer-tiktok-won-145816473.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:buyer for TikTok (whom he did not name);cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">buyer for TikTok (whom he did not name)</a>, President Donald Trump he did not think he would need to extend a July 9 tariffs deadline, Bloomberg reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>    <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-says-doesn-t-expect-152200922.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Read more here</a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"e6007300-023e-48bb-bd76-2c6c7a1998e8\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Sat, June 28, 2025 at 9:05 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Associated Press</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Fourth of July fireworks displays won\'t be impacted by tariffs this year. Next year might be a different story.</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->As the Independence Day holiday approaches, the fireworks used in displays across the US likely won\'t be affected by President Trump\'s tariffs, at least, not yet. A 90-day pause on the levies slated for imports from China is in effect, but such tariffs would hit the fireworks industry hard. Nearly all the fireworks used in the US are imported from China, the Associated Press reports.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The price tag on future fireworks displays, however, are up in the air:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>     <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/fireworks-light-fourth-july-next-040420305.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here</em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>   <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-5\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-5 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_5\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div> <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"0a183c60-bd65-47d6-b5a0-5a073b024e24\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/NGAdksx9mI7EOCPDxur9DA--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2F36118300-c417-11e9-b3a3-135760195748&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=4d2f3e0cb5fbdb522dc15f4c4881f3c11f1dc917\" alt=\"Ben Werschkul\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Sat, June 28, 2025 at 6:14 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Ben Werschkul</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">\'We can do whatever we want\': Trump sows confusion on his summer tariff timeline</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The market\'s task of planning for how tariff developments will play out this summer got more complicated Friday as President Trump and his team offered a host of options for what to expect in the months ahead.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->First, Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent raised eyebrows <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.foxbusiness.com/video/6374941242112\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:when he suggested;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">when he suggested</a> that his focus could be on an end-of-summer deadline, saying, \"I think we could have trade wrapped up by Labor Day.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->But any hopes for a summer lull between now and then were short-lived when, just a few hours later, Trump offered multiple other scenarios during a wide-ranging press conference.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->At one point, the president reiterated his plan to send letters to dictate tariff rates for at least some countries, perhaps as soon as next week, saying, \"It\'s going to go very quickly.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Minutes later, he said that a July 9 deadline to raise \"reciprocal\" tariffs is not set and perhaps could move, but in an unpredictable direction.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"We can do whatever we want,\" he told reporters of that deadline. \"We could extend it, we could make it shorter,\" adding that his preference was to make it shorter.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/we-can-do-whatever-we-want-trump-sows-confusion-on-his-summer-tariff-timeline-182901280.html?\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here</em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"34518ed3-9824-4b4f-b9ac-8727fef3460c\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/g1RR1MwDLfI3hCRmTPYyTg--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-05%2F128dd290-f595-11ed-b4d8-cbe5a3d4e16f&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=4032c266a6e3ad3af35e07e05b7f14a19b6e7fcb\" alt=\"Brett LoGiurato\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 6:21 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Brett LoGiurato</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Trump says he\'s cutting off trade talks with Canada</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->President Trump on Friday said he is cutting off all trade talks with Canada, threatening to set a new tariff rate on goods imported from the country within the next week.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The reason, according to Trump: Canada\'s plan to implement a digital services tax, which could affect US tech companies.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Trump\'s about-face throws a potential wrench in weeks of trade progress. Just hours earlier, the US and China cemented the trade truce first agreed to last month in Geneva.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Here\'s Trump\'s Truth Social post on Canada, in full:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> </div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"7b78cd74-82c2-4a26-badc-c32b903ea04a\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 5:04 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Grace O\'Donnell</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">President Trump leaves question over July 9 tariff deadline open</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->On Friday afternoon, President Trump touted tariff revenue and an influx of domestic manufacturing but offered few details on the state of tariff negotiations ahead of the July 9 deadline, when the tariff pause expires.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The president acknowledged that the administration won\'t be able to reach deals with 200-plus countries over the next week and a half. But he did not definitively say whether tariff rates would jump back up to \"Liberation Day\" levels.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"We can do whatever we want,\" Trump told reporters in a press briefing, referring to the tariff pause. \"We could extend it. We could make it shorter ‚Äî I\'d like to make it shorter. I\'d like to just send letters out to everybody: \'Congratulations, you\'re paying 25%\'\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>  <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->So far, the Trump administration has confirmed preliminary trade agreements with China (as of today) and the UK. Trump noted that officials are in the process of negotiating other deals, which he said are \"going to go very quickly.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->In particular, Trump again teased a potential deal with India, which has faced roadblocks in recent weeks over some of the country\'s protectionist policies for certain sectors.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"Some of the bigger countries, India, I think we\'re going to reach a deal where we have the right to go in and trade,\" Trump said. \"Right now, it\'s restricted. ... We\'re looking to get a full trade barrier dropping, which is unthinkable, and I\'m not sure that that\'s going to happen, but as of this moment, we\'ve agreed to go into Indian trade.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>   <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-6\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-6 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_6\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div> <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"22da2f29-3667-4cb4-8c06-942d5b8dc945\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/g1RR1MwDLfI3hCRmTPYyTg--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-05%2F128dd290-f595-11ed-b4d8-cbe5a3d4e16f&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=4032c266a6e3ad3af35e07e05b7f14a19b6e7fcb\" alt=\"Brett LoGiurato\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 4:07 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Brett LoGiurato</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">US, EU confident of reaching a deal by July 9 deadline</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->US and EU officials are confident of clinching a trade deal before a July 9 deadline, <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/eu-us-confident-ll-reach-145304800.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Bloomberg reported Friday;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Bloomberg reported Friday</a>.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Amid continued progress on China, the US-EU talks have come in high focus ahead of that deadline, with US tariffs of up to 50% looming on EU imports.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->From the report:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>     <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/eu-us-confident-ll-reach-145304800.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here</em></a>.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"3bd05d7a-cc68-45c5-823c-62c51ed7629e\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 12:41 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Grace O\'Donnell</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Bessent: \'We could have trade wrapped up by Labor Day\'</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent said on Friday that the US could wrap up its most important trade deals by Labor Day.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->\"Secretary Lutnick said yesterday that he expects 10 more deals,\" Bessent told Fox Business Network in an interview. \"So if we can ink 10 or 12 of the important 18, there are another important 20 relationships, then I think we could have trade wrapped up by Labor Day.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bessent\'s comments come after the US and China signed an interim trade agreement on Friday that would reduce tariffs while the two sides work toward a formal deal.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Trump administration officials have softened their stance toward the July 9 deadline they set for themselves to hammer out trade pacts. On Thursday, White House press secretary Karoline Leavitt said the early July deadline \"is not critical\" while Trump\'s top economic adviser said he expected the US to extend the pause for countries negotiating \"in good faith.\"<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"08bce015-5f86-41ab-b0f6-f70dd5de7410\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 11:44 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Karen Friar</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">China confirms details of trade framework laid out by US</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The other shoe has dropped: Beijing has backed up the plans for trade easing laid out by the US, signaling warmer relations between the recently feuding sides.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bloomberg reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>     <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/china-confirms-us-trade-framework-081543235.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here</em></a>.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>   <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-7\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-7 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_7\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div> <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"66e15d6f-eef7-440f-88ed-bcd628e218dd\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><img class=\"avatar yf-1ebdqmb\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/dv.VTTSch3jvXf1wCG7ZLg--~B/Zmk9ZmlsbDtoPTQwO3B5b2ZmPTA7dz00MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-04%2F41fcc720-f5a8-11ee-bbe2-e9cb8cdc4c82&amp;compress=1&amp;progressive=1&amp;quality=75&amp;client=hawkeye&amp;signature=3e3930835cf0e3365df3a70c112b3755056f7bf7\" alt=\"Brian Sozzi\"></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 9:35 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Brian Sozzi</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block  with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Don\'t think tariffs sting? Ask Nike!</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Nike (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NKE\" data-ylk=\"slk:NKE;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">NKE</a>) slipped this one into its earnings call last night: It could see a $1 billion tariff hit to profits this year!<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->How does it plan to overcome that, you ask? By jacking up prices even more soon. How the consumer responds to the higher prices will determine if the tariff hit is a greater-than-expected weight on the business.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Keep that risk in mind as the big premarket move excites you.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->We\'ll dive more into Nike\'s quarter on <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/live/\" data-ylk=\"slk:Opening Bid live;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">Opening Bid live</a> at 9:30 a.m ET.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"d8f2eb27-0808-4421-91db-dd364e463ec9\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 9:05 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Karen Friar</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Trump teases \'big\' India trade deal despite talks deadlock</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->President Trump has said the US could sign a ‚Äúvery big‚Äù trade deal soon that would open up the Indian market to American businesses, even as both sides meet in D.C. to break a recent deadlock over key issues.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bloomberg reports:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>    <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-teases-big-india-trade-043507944.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Read more here</a>.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"4982c346-7037-4cf0-a92c-3e5150714fb0\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Fri, June 27, 2025 at 4:56 AM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Rian Howlett</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">Trump confirms US-China trade truce, claims global tariff deals incoming</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->President Trump said Thursday that the US and China have \"signed\" a trade deal, cementing months-long negotiations. The deal builds on meetings in Geneva between representatives of both nations and implements measures previously agreed upon.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->‚ÄúWe just signed with China yesterday,‚Äù Trump said during remarks at the White House, without offering specifics. A White House official later clarified that both nations had agreed to a framework to implement the <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-and-xi-break-the-ice-in-long-awaited-call-agree-to-restart-trade-talks-134121780.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Geneva truce first negotiated in May;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">Geneva truce first negotiated in May</a>.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->In that truce, the US and China agreed to a 90-day reduction in tariffs while working toward a formal deal. Talks had stalled over issues such as US export controls and China‚Äôs rare earth exports.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Earlier this month, Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent, Commerce Secretary Howard Lutnick, and Trade Representative Jamieson Greer met in London with Chinese Vice Premier He Lifeng. Following two days of negotiations, the parties said they had reached an agreement<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->‚ÄúThey‚Äôre going to deliver rare earths to us,‚Äù <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-06-26/us-china-have-finalized-tariff-understanding-lutnick-says?srnd=homepage-americas\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:Lutnick said in an interview with Bloomberg;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" class=\"link \">Lutnick said in an interview with Bloomberg</a>. \"We\'ll take down our countermeasures\", he added.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->The announcement comes a deadline looms for the US to reimpose tariffs of up to 50% on several trading partners by July 9 unless the countries reach permanent agreements. Lutnick has hinted that deals are incoming with the largest trade partners. \"We‚Äôre going to do top 10 deals, put them in the right category, and then these other countries will fit behind,\" he said.<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>   <div id=\"sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-8\" class=\"sdaContainer  dv-all sda-INARTICLE-3e71054e-63ef-419f-90ec-5357f8c99ad3-8 yf-1m4k8v7 overflow margin  visible placeholder\" data-testid=\"ad-container\" data-ad-unit=\"/22888152279/us/yfin/ros/dt/us_yfin_ros_dt_mid_center\" data-ad-size=\"970x250,728x90,300x250\" data-ad-region=\"main-dynamic\" data-ad-loc=\"mid_center_8\" style=\"--placeholder-height: 250px;\"></div> <li class=\"caas-liveblogpost yf-1ebdqmb\" id=\"3c88e32e-ac24-433f-8ac5-55cc963de21d\" data-testid=\"blog-post\"><div class=\"liveblogposts-post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"post yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"timeline-point no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"circles yf-1ebdqmb\" data-svelte-h=\"svelte-1fe2nsg\"><div class=\"oval-back yf-1ebdqmb\"></div> <div class=\"oval yf-1ebdqmb\"></div></div></div> <div class=\"timestamp-byline yf-1ebdqmb\"><time class=\"timestamp-most-recent yf-1ebdqmb liveblogpost-relative-time\">Thu, June 26, 2025 at 9:41 PM UTC</time> <div class=\"byline-meta yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"byline yf-1ebdqmb\">Amalya Dubrovsky</div></div></div> </div> <div class=\"content-wrapper no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-body yf-1ebdqmb\"><div class=\"content-block no-pfp with-author-name yf-1ebdqmb\"><h2 class=\"headline yf-1ebdqmb\">EU leaders consider Trump\'s latest trade proposal</h2>  <div class=\"body yf-1ebdqmb\"> <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Bloomberg <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/eu-briefs-divided-leaders-trump-203513677.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:reports;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\">reports</a>:<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p>      <p class=\"yf-1090901\"><!-- HTML_TAG_START --><a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/eu-briefs-divided-leaders-trump-203513677.html\" data-ylk=\"slk:Read more here.;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" class=\"link  yahoo-link\"><em>Read more here.</em></a><!-- HTML_TAG_END --></p></div></div></div></div></div> </li>  </ul> </div>  <div class=\"liveblog-showmore yf-jncdpv\"><div class=\"gradient yf-jncdpv\"></div> <button class=\"secondary-btn fin-size-large   rounded   yf-1epmntv\" data-ylk=\"elm:btn;slk:Story%20Continues;sec:liveblog;itc:1\"> Story Continues</button></div>  </div>     </div></div> <span class=\"article-footer yf-10hzt8r\"><section class=\"privacy-container yf-1uw5cxs inline\" style=\"--privacy-link-font-weight: var(--font-normal);\"><div class=\"terms-and-privacy small yf-1uw5cxs column\"><a class=\"subtle-link fin-size-small privacy-link-terms-link     yf-u4gyzs\" data-ylk=\"elm:corp;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:article;subsec:footer\" href=\"https://guce.yahoo.com/terms?locale=en-US\">Terms  </a> an